  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">This Privacy Policy explains how JOMSEARCH collects and uses information when you use our search engine and related services.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1) What we collect</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
    <li><span class="font-medium">Search data:</span> your search queries and basic usage events (e.g., clicks on results) to improve relevance and quality.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">Device & app data:</span> browser type, language, approximate location (from IP), and performance diagnostics.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">Cookies/local storage:</span> small files used to remember preferences like theme, region, or recent searches.</li>
    <li><span class="font-medium">Optional account data:</span> if you create an account, we store your email and settings. Accounts are optional.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2) How we use data</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
    <li>Deliver search results and features like safe search, language, and region.</li>
    <li>Measure performance and fix bugs.</li>
    <li>Prevent abuse, spam, and security incidents.</li>
    <li>Improve ranking, spelling correction, and result quality.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3) Analytics & third parties</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700">We may use privacy‑focused analytics and integrate with search APIs to fetch results. When you click a result, you leave JOMSEARCH and the destination website’s policies apply.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4) Ads</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700">If we display ads, they may be contextual (based on your query) rather than based on your identity. We do not sell personal information.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5) Data retention</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700">Search logs are kept for a limited period necessary for security and product improvement, then aggregated or deleted. Account data is kept until you delete your account.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6) Your choices</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
    <li>Use JOMSEARCH without an account.</li>
    <li>Adjust preferences (e.g., safe search, region).</li>
    <li>Request export or deletion of account data by contacting us.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">7) Children</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700">JOMSEARCH is not intended for children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal data, contact us to delete it.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">8) Changes</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700">We may update this Policy. Changes take effect when posted here. We will update the “Last updated” date below.</p>

  <div class="mt-8 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">Last updated: 2025-08-19</div></br>
